Enter the Chef Express world and discover the benefits dedicated to you!

With the new APP you can access all the exclusive services reserved for Chef Express customers from your smartphone.

To start, register and immediately access your personalized loyalty program.

Through our application you can:
- access your virtual card at any time and obtain discounts and promotions reserved for you;
- stay up to date on the status of your profile;
- access the Webcam Park service;
- request the invoice for each transaction;
- find the store closest to you, and be informed about opening hours and services;
- access dedicated promotions;
- access the Booking Groups service to book your group parking in comfort

Download the APP and discover the customized program dedicated to your needs!

Put our products to the test, exploit their great features and cook an unlimited number of menus!

The De’Longhi Recipe Book is the new, free App - for smartphones and tablets - collecting all the recipes for your De’Longhi cooking appliances. 
The De’Longhi Recipe Book is a complete cooking tool:
● a large, and always increasing, number of recipes;
● easy-to-use, can be taken everywhere;
● with recipes from all over the world;
● all recipes tested by a chef;
● eat better with direct control on calories;
● share your cooking experience with your friends through social networks;
● save your Favourites in the dedicated area.
